title: John and Oscar Get Good. Second video feedback please!

embed.description: This time we use pure support tactics to get a Quadra at ten minutes. League of Legends is made by Riot games.

body: Hey guys we made another video! Any feedback is appreciated and we hope you enjoy!

replies.body: I like some parts of the video, like that sweet braum quadra, I think you should focus more on highlights though
Okay awesome! We can do that as editing isn't too bad. Thank you for your feedback!
